---
title: Harissa Chicken Breasts and Chickpea Stew with Spiced Flatbread Crisps and Feta
description: Chicken and chickpeas get a North African-style treatment in this hearty and fragrant stew. You'll love dunking the spiced flatbread crisps into this protein-packed wonder!
